3) Profile & Objekt-Modell (vereinfachtes Datenmodell)

User: id, name, email, locale, roles[], org_ids[], consents{}, privacyPrefs{}

Organization (Unternehmen): id, name, legal, brands[], locations[], publicationPolicy{}

Brand (Marke): id, org_id, name, tone, assets, visibilitySettings{}

Location (Standort): id, brand_id, address, hours, gmb_id, ig_id, …, publicationFlags{}

RoleBinding: user_id, scope_type(org|brand|location), scope_id, role

ContentItem (Post/Asset/Story): id, scope, status (draft|pending|approved|published), sensitivityTags[] (persönlich/sensibel), approvalTrail[]

Voucher: code, type(test|30d-full), status, recipient_email, expires_at, redeemed_by_user_id

AuditEvent: actor(user/agent), action, scope, payload_hash, result, timestamp